sequenceDiagram
  actor U as User
  participant R as Route
  participant H as Hook
  participant SF as Server Fn
  participant DB as Postgres

  U->>R: Navigate to page
  R->>H: Render + request data
  H->>SF: Call server function
  SF->>SF: Validate + authorize request
  SF->>DB: Run query/mutation
  DB-->>SF: Result rows
  SF-->>H: DTO response
  H-->>R: Cache + provide data
  R-->>U: Render UI / updates

